content:
Service Process Automation helps you streamline and automate service-related operations. The core component is Service Process Studio, a framework that lets you design case-driven service processes.

Available in Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled.

Service Process Studio helps you design customer service processes quickly and efficiently. Service agents can launch these processes and get started with the customer service operations.

Implementing effective service processes is a key factor for customer satisfaction. Building service processes and configuring integrations is a time-consuming task.

Retail Banking, Wealth Management, and Self Service are available as unmanaged packages.

Let your customer community users initiate service processes directly from a self-service portal, such as the Financial Services Client Portal.

Integrate Service Process Studio with Product Catalog Management to enable controlled access for service processes. Configure customer eligibility rules and user access control so that users see only relevant service processes in the Action Launcher.
title: Service Process Automation for Financial Services Cloud
